  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd ; 24 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Protest by laying siege to the Prime Minister's office; 24 people were injured",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "24 people were injured in the anti-government protest in front of the Prime Minister's office.",
        "Colombo - The protest took place in front of the Prime Minister's office located at 7 Flower Street today, Wednesday.",
        "Meanwhile, the Prime Minister's office was besieged by the protesters and the protesters seized the Prime Minister's office after the protest."
      ],
